when the scandal

00:18:11.020 --> 00:18:12.420
about Dafu Jewelry
swapping high-quality stones

00:18:12.660 --> 00:18:13.900
for inferior ones broke out,

00:18:14.220 --> 00:18:16.660
I had no idea they were in my warehouse.

00:18:17.820 --> 00:18:19.020
By the time I found out,

00:18:20.580 --> 00:18:21.740
your mother

00:18:22.140 --> 00:18:23.940
had already taken her own life
because of this.

00:18:25.820 --> 00:18:27.100
If I had come forward then,

00:18:27.460 --> 00:18:29.300
I'd have had no way to clear my name.

00:18:31.140 --> 00:18:31.700
Yes.

00:18:33.180 --> 00:18:34.780
I investigated in Italy too.

00:18:36.180 --> 00:18:38.420
The rough gemstones were picked up
by an Asian man.

00:18:38.700 --> 00:18:39.820
Paid in cash.

00:18:40.260 --> 00:18:41.660
I got the transaction records.

00:18:43.100 --> 00:18:44.660
There was
no signature of yours on them...

00:18:44.700 --> 00:18:45.940
But those gemstones

00:18:46.460 --> 00:18:48.700
did end up in my warehouse.

00:18:51.380 --> 00:18:54.420
I never dared to touch or sell

00:18:54.820 --> 00:18:55.940
those gemstones.

00:18:56.700 --> 00:18:58.300
I've always kept them in the warehouse.

00:18:59.500 --> 00:19:01.060
To avoid drawing attention,

00:19:01.660 --> 00:19:04.420
I even listed them as inferior quality.

00:19:05.180 --> 00:19:06.580
Some time ago,

00:19:06.820 --> 00:19:09.540
Yi Wenhan developed a low-end series

00:19:10.020 --> 00:19:11.620
and used those gemstones.

00:19:11.820 --> 00:19:12.780
When I found out,

00:19:13.020 --> 00:19:14.540
I immediately
called off this product line

00:19:14.580 --> 00:19:15.780
and sealed up all the bulk goods!

00:19:18.340 --> 00:19:19.340
Baijian,

00:19:21.220 --> 00:19:23.620
I really didn't swap
your family's rough gemstones.

00:19:26.100 --> 00:19:28.060
Yes, Dafu Jewelry's downfall

00:19:28.900 --> 00:19:30.540
helped Starlight Jewelry rise.

00:19:31.540 --> 00:19:32.580
But I

00:19:33.140 --> 00:19:35.060
am not that kind of vile man!

00:19:37.180 --> 00:19:38.620
I can swear to you.

00:19:39.340 --> 00:19:41.620
If I had anything to do
with your family's gemstones,

00:19:42.060 --> 00:19:43.140
may I rot in the grave!

00:19:55.300 --> 00:19:56.460
Then tell me,

00:19:57.940 --> 00:19:59.660
who was it that framed you?

00:19:59.860 --> 00:20:00.660
If you know anything,

00:20:00.740 --> 00:20:01.820
you must tell me.

00:20:02.980 --> 00:20:04.300
For our sake,

00:20:05.260 --> 00:20:06.260
and for Zhizhi's.

00:20:11.460 --> 00:20:12.660
I have no proof,

00:20:14.140 --> 00:20:15.540
but the person who benefited the most

00:20:16.260 --> 00:20:17.340
from that incident

00:20:18.340 --> 00:20:20.220
was the chairman of Starlight Group,

00:20:20.820 --> 00:20:21.620
Ye Taiting.

00:20:26.460 --> 00:20:27.460
Baijian.

00:20:28.980 --> 00:20:30.020
Whatever you do,

00:20:32.220 --> 00:20:33.100
please

00:20:33.940 --> 00:20:35.260
don't hurt Zhizhi

00:20:36.340 --> 00:20:37.420
because of this.

00:20:40.780 --> 00:20:41.620
Don't worry.

00:20:42.900 --> 00:20:44.260
It was entirely my own decision

00:20:44.740 --> 00:20:45.860
to be with Zhizhi

00:20:47.060 --> 00:20:48.300
and marry her.

00:21:20.820 --> 00:21:21.540
Zhizhi.

00:21:24.340 --> 00:21:25.500
How did you know I was here?

00:21:26.660 --> 00:21:27.740
I just saw your father.

00:21:29.180 --> 00:21:30.780
We talked everything through
about what happened back then.

00:21:31.980 --> 00:21:33.220
Whether you want to hear it or not,

00:21:33.900 --> 00:21:35.180
I need to explain.

00:21:37.820 --> 00:21:38.340
Fine.

00:21:41.100 --> 00:21:41.820
Go ahead.

00:21:42.340 --> 00:21:43.820
I'd love to hear

00:21:45.260 --> 00:21:46.940
what excuse you've come up with.

00:21:49.300 --> 00:21:50.500
Here's the thing.

00:21:51.260 --> 00:21:52.980
My mother designed
a piece of jewelry back then,

00:21:53.540 --> 00:21:54.700
but the rough gemstones were swapped.

00:21:56.380 --> 00:21:58.020
When the scandal broke
about the inferior stones,

00:21:58.700 --> 00:22:00.580
she was bombarded
with a torrent of abuse.

00:22:02.180 --> 00:22:03.140
My mother's death

00:22:03.140 --> 00:22:04.140
made my father furious.

00:22:04.700 --> 00:22:06.100
He vowed to find the culprit

00:22:06.100 --> 00:22:07.100
and get revenge.

00:22:07.580 --> 00:22:09.020
So he wanted me to use
the arranged marriage

00:22:09.020 --> 00:22:10.060
to investigate your family.

00:22:11.380 --> 00:22:13.420
I... I'd been living abroad.

00:22:13.740 --> 00:22:14.780
I didn't know you.

00:22:15.740 --> 00:22:17.620
So when he asked me, I agreed.

00:22:21.780 --> 00:22:22.940
But as I got to know you,

00:22:22.940 --> 00:22:23.700
I started to understand you

00:22:25.140 --> 00:22:25.900
and I fell in love with you.

00:22:27.660 --> 00:22:28.740
I love you, Zhizhi.

00:22:33.460 --> 00:22:34.500
My love for you is real.

00:22:34.500 --> 00:22:35.780
It has nothing to do with revenge.

00:22:35.780 --> 00:22:37.180
I really want to be with you.

00:22:40.940 --> 00:22:41.820
Really?

00:22:41.840 --> 00:22:44.700
♪Baby, asleep? Don't reply♪

00:22:44.700 --> 00:22:45.860
Then why, in all this time

00:22:45.860 --> 00:22:47.220
we've been together,

00:22:48.020 --> 00:22:49.460
did you never once mention any of this?

00:22:51.140 --> 00:22:52.340
How am I supposed to believe you?

00:22:54.060 --> 00:22:54.740
My bad.

00:22:56.740 --> 00:22:57.620
It's my fault.

00:22:58.340 --> 00:22:59.660
I should have told you sooner.

00:23:00.460 --> 00:23:01.460
I thought about it,

00:23:02.140 --> 00:23:03.700
but I never found the right moment.

00:23:03.700 --> 00:23:07.820
♪There's a dreamscape
where I still call your name♪

00:23:07.820 --> 00:23:08.380
Sorry.

00:23:11.060 --> 00:23:12.140
I'm so sorry, Zhizhi.

00:23:12.260 --> 00:23:12.900
I was wrong.

00:23:14.060 --> 00:23:15.460
Can you give me another chance?

00:23:16.390 --> 00:23:18.940
♪Yet through the pain,
I'll never leave your side♪

00:23:18.940 --> 00:23:20.180
I've already figured it out.

00:23:20.180 --> 00:23:20.940
I believe your father.

00:23:21.980 --> 00:23:23.580
The stolen gemstones had nothing to do
with the Song family.

00:23:23.620 --> 00:23:25.100
I'll explain everything to my father.

00:23:26.460 --> 00:23:28.100
I think someone else is behind this,
setting you up.

00:23:28.980 --> 00:23:29.980
Setting me up?

