♪Hold me tight.
Don't let go of this dream♪

00:23:34.500 --> 00:23:35.420
Wasn't it you

00:23:36.660 --> 00:23:38.100
who's been setting me up,

00:23:39.260 --> 00:23:40.620
Ji Baijian?

